This directory contains code specific to SCFT calculations.

Subdirectories:

iterator/    - classes to implement SCFT iteration algorithms
sweep/       - classes to peform a sweep through parameter space

C++ Files:

System.h      - System<D> class template header (main object)
System.tpp    - System<D> class template definition
System.cpp    - System<D> explicit instantiations for D=1,2,3

Makefile and makefile fragments:

sources.mk    - list of source files (makefile fragment)
makefile      - main makefile for rpg/scft directory tree

Doxygen documentation files:

scft.mod      - defintion of the Rpg_Scft doxygen module

